{"tid":2201023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[塔羅]有無咩問題想問？","createTime":"2020-09-13T12:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T07:24:40.000Z","uid":216779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e45373d897531a011221feee5cecdd2407151e4d","tid":2201023,"uid":216779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"塔羅新手想練習下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問野可以寫低問題同留低tg<br />\n我再搵你<br />\n<br />\n問既問題最好具體d<br />\n咁樣解牌既時候 答案都會更精準<br />\n可以睇到更多野去幫大家<br />\n<br />\nEg: 想問下幾時先有女朋友？（X)<br />\n》三個月內會唔會搵到女朋友 / 符合我條件既人出現？<br />\n<br />\n再舉個例<br />\n<br />\nEg: 我同佢仲有無緣份？（X)<br />\n》佢仲中唔中意我？仲有無可能發展關係？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塔羅牌連結到潛意識所以有一定準確度<br />\n但未必會係100%準確 <br />\n睇到短期內既野同發展可能<br />\n帶返個頭盔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085e20064b8b75aaf819a06e6638900046e65ffa","tid":2201023,"uid":359263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/lunyiihum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flunyiihum&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8L2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c5d38ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lunyiihum</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒ching"},{"pid":"b8e9c3adbc0c493fb1930221e5cefcfec8de3b5c","tid":2201023,"uid":307862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d4484be72b2675bfc44b1242d84d7edeecd0a8","tid":2201023,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6107b74fda0d9ecff7a8bde93e6f706b6111d15","tid":2201023,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed44c95fe0a17adf2d4b9b6ff192c904c619a486","tid":2201023,"uid":196699,"like":0,"dis